OL,3,C'Mentally, it's painful' - Shop owner
OL,4,Cin despair after rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FKent Police are promising tougher
OL,7,Faction on shoplifters as figures
OL,8,Freveal the crime is at some of its
OL,9,Fhighest levels within the last decade.
OL,11,FRetailers say the problem is having a
OL,12,Fdetrimental impact on their lives,
OL,13,Fboth mentally and financially - with
OL,14,Fone shopkeeper in Medway telling us he
OL,15,Fregularly can't sleep, worrying about
OL,16,Fhis store.
OL,18,FEven with cameras at his two stores,
OL,19,Fthieves are costing Gobal Rajendran
OL,20,Fthousands of pounds and there is a
OL,21,Fprice to his wellbeing too.
