OL,3,C'Mentally, it's painful' - Shop owner
OL,4,Cin despair after rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FBusiness owner, Gobal Rajendran said:
OL,7,F"Before it would be one a month and
OL,8,Fnow it's 10 a month, even last week it
OL,9,Fwas three times in one week.
OL,11,F"Mentally, it's painful. When I close
OL,12,Fthe store at 10 o clock and I go to
OL,13,Fsleep, I'm still remembering and
OL,14,Fthinking, 'why are people doing this?'
OL,16,FMore than 15,000 offences were
OL,17,Frecorded, in the past 12 months to
OL,18,FMarch 2024, compared to just under
OL,19,F13,000 in 2023, which is 20% increase.
