OL,3,C'Mentally, it's painful' - Shop owner
OL,4,Cin despair after rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FSupt Peter Steenhuis, Kent Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've also seen there's been a
OL,8,F22% increase in bringing people to
OL,9,Fjustice
OL,11,F"Every time we bring someone to
OL,12,Fjustice, we can either put them on our
OL,13,Fintegrated offender management
OL,14,Fprojects, to make sure we divert them
OL,15,Faway from that crime, or we can deal
OL,16,Fwith them in other ways through the
OL,17,Fcriminal justice system to reduce
OL,18,Ftheir offending going forward.
