OL,6,FProlific thief Tommy Robertson has had
OL,7,Fa banning order imposed, he's not
OL,8,Fallowed near any business in Tunbridge
OL,9,FWells for two years after stealing
OL,10,Fdesigner items.
OL,12,FJesse Barton is not allowed to visit
OL,13,Fsupermarkets across Ashford for three
OL,14,Fyears, on one occasion he was caught
OL,15,F#169 worth of biscuits.
OL,17,FThe county's police and crime
OL,18,Fcommissioner acknowledges more can be
OL,19,Fdone and wants to improve trust
OL,20,Fbetween the force and affected
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
