OL,6,FMatthew Scott, Kent Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner said: "We're increasing
OL,8,Fthe level of resources for officers on
OL,9,Fthe beat.
OL,11,F"Our beat officers are working with
OL,12,Fretailers, helping building up their
OL,13,Fprofile and supporting them .
OL,15,F"We're increasing the number of
OL,16,Foffences being solved and putting more
OL,17,Fpeople before the courts, so we have a
OL,18,Fvery good proactive strategy for
OL,19,Finvestigating shoplifting and
